{
  "stem": "11844.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they went through that underground tunnel and were picked up by us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And one day, Laura Doller and I, we took our train from Amsterdam to Assen-- that was the big city in that area.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we had our two bicycles on the train.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we were supposed to pick up two people-- Gerhardt Wunch and Hans Oster.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we left the station, Assen, with our bicycles, and went towards Hooghalen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Hooghalen is the little village which is close to the camp Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Laura and I, we were pedalling on our bicycles.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we come to Hooghalen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I see two [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] is the same like-- it's not police, a very special police.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in the [INAUDIBLE], there were comparatively many Nazis.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the police department, hardly any.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But in the [INAUDIBLE] were many.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was very, very worried, because they looked at us like this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I knew there was an old German general of the 19th century.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He used to say, the best defense is attack.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I attacked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went to those two police officers and asked them for-- what is the shortest way to go to Hooghalen?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he looked at me, and he said, in Dutch, [SPEAKING DUTCH].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Which means, in English, 'You guys are foreigners from Jerusalem.' Which is an old Dutch expression which I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But when he said, you are foreigners from Jerusalem, I thought, my gosh, the son of a bitch knew we are Jews and now we are dead.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he explained the way to me and I told Laura what he said.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she started to laugh and explained to me, there's an old Dutch expression.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
